    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>You attended an event. Write an article for your blog.</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>Hi everybody,</p>
                <p/>
                <p>This sunday afternoon I will organise a party in my garden. The weather should be nice, so coming! You just have to bring your personal drink, I will cook for you. Everybody like hot-dog? I think it's the more simple.</p>
                <p>If you want, you can invite your friends but please ask me before.</p>
                <p>My parents won't be at home, don't worry.</p>
                <p>The swimmingpool will be open, so don't forget to bring your stuffs to go in.</p>
                <p>You can come at 12a.m and the party will finish at 03p.m</p>
                <p/>
                <p>I hope to see you all.</p>
                <p/>
                <p>xoxo</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
